40:40.913 --> 40:42.951
Amy: WELCOME TO
THE FIRST GENERATION.

40:46.458 --> 40:48.229
[ THUDDING CONTINUES ]

40:52.371 --> 40:55.979
[ THUDDING INTENSIFIES ]

41:02.927 --> 41:04.932
[ THUDDING STOPS ]

41:04.932 --> 41:07.504
I'M NOT ASKING
